Kim-ku3: Sin3 e5 lang5 long2 chit8-sim chit8-i3, ...... tak8-hang7 mih8 choe3 kong--e5. (Su3-tou5 heng7-toan7 4:32)
Thau5-su5:
Chhou-tai7 e5 sin3-tou5, in hoe2-kai2 kui Chu2 liau2-au7, chin jiat8-sim lai5 kun-toe3 tng-si5 e5 sin3-tou5 tiong. In sim7-chi3 soa3 chiong sou2 u7 e5 chinn5-chai5 but8-chit, long2-chong2 hong7-hian3 ti7 cheng3 hiann-ti7 tiong, choe3 kong-kiong7 e5 lou7-eng7. Lan2 na7 thiann3 Chu2, chiu7 oe7 sinn-chhut chit-teng2-ho7 bo5 su-khia, hi-seng sio2-ngou2, seng5-choan5 tai7-ngou2 e5 cheng-sin5.
Kou3-su7: ¡§Tang3-sng e5 Sio2-lim5¡¨
Ti7 chit8-keng kau3-hoe7 e5 Chu2-jit8-oh8, u7 chit8-e5 gin2-na2 kio3-choe3 ¡§tang3-sng e5 Sio2-lim5¡¨. Sio2-lim5 chai ai3 chinn5, ia7-si7 chin tang3-sng. I m7-ai3 hong7-hian3, m7-ai3 pang-chan7 pat8-lang5, i siong5-siong5 tui3 a-pa a-bu2 tho2 chinn5, kong2 beh ti7 le2-pai3-jit8 hian3-kim, chong2-si7 long2 bo5-iann2, si7 khi3 lok8 ti7 su-khia, pi3-bit8 e5 chinn5-tang5-a2 nih8, sou2-i2 an2-ni i e5 chinn5-tang5-a2, chiu7 chiam7-chiam7 moa2 khi2-lai5. U7 chit8-mi5 i teh siunn7 i e5 chinn5 tioh8 lai5 cho3 sim2-mih8 lou7-eng7, be2 sui2 e5 sann? Bo5-ai3, a-bu2 oe7 be2 hou7 goa2, be2 thit-tho5 mih8? M7-bian2, goa2 thang tui3 a-i5, a-chek iau3-kiu5. Kiat-kiok8 tang3-sng e5 Sio2-lim5 chiu7 chiong hiah e5 chinn5 koh siu khi2-lai5.
U7 chit8 le2-pai3, ti7 Chu2-jit8-oh8 lau7-su kong2, Seng3-tan3 beh kau3 lah, ai3 be2 sann lai5 sang3 hou7 lou7-pinn e5 khit-chiah8, sou2-i2 chhiann2 tai7-ke chin7-lat8 hong7-hian3. Sio2-lim5 siunn7 kong2 an2-ni chin bo5-chhai2. Koh chit8-pai2, kau3-hoe7 u7 chit8-ui7 kho2-lin5 bo5 i-oa2 e5 lau7-lang5 phoa3-pinn7, lau7-su ai3 tai7-ke ui7-tioh8 i hong7-hian3 thang pang-chan7 i, Sio2-lim5 khiok siunn7 an2-ni si7 chin phah-sng2. Chi2-u7 i e5 chinn5-tang5-a2 jit8-jit8 it-tit8 tinn7 khi2-lai5.
U7 chit8-me5-hng Sio2-lim5 teh khun3 e5 si5, u7 khoann3-kinn3 chit8 e5 chheng7 phoa3-noa7 e5 sann, koann5 kau3 chhun-chhiu2 tui3 i kiu5-khit kong2, ¡§Tang3-sng e5 Sio2-lim5, chhiann2 li2 kho2-lin5 goa2!¡¨ Khiok Sio2-lim5 tioh8 chit8-kiann, kin2-kin2 chiong chinn5-tang5-a2 lam2-oa2 khi2-lai5 kong2, ¡§Bo5-chhai2, bo5-chhai2, che si7 goa2 e5 chinn5, bo5-ai3 hou7 li2!¡¨ Hit e5 thang kiann e5 khit-chiah8 tit8-tit8 pek oa2-khi3, hou7 Sio2-lim5 thoe3 kau3 long2 bo5 ui7. Kou-put-chiong, in-ui7 kiann-hiann5, Sio2-lim5 chiu7 khui chinn5-tang5-a2, tui3 hit lai7-bin7 chhiau-chhoe7 chit8-tiunn phoa3-noa7, beh tng7 cho3 koeh8 e5 gin5-phio3 hiat hou7 i. Hit e5 khit-chiah8 chiu7 pian3-choe3 chit8 e5 chin sui2 e5 thinn-sai3, tui3 Sio2-lim5 seh-sai7, lai5 pian3 bo5-khi3.
Sio2-lim5 khai-si2 ui7-tioh8 i hit e5 phoa3-noa7 e5 gin5-phio3 kam2-kak bo5-chhai2 lai5 siong-sim.
Tng i koh teh khun3 e5 si5, tang3-sng e5 Sio2-lim5 chiu7 koh khoann3-kinn3, u7 chit8 e5 tai3 tang7-pinn7 soe-jiok8 e5 lau7-lang5 khia7 ti7 i e5 chhng5-cheng5, chhun-chhiu2 tui3 i ai-kiu5 kong2, ¡§Tang3-sng e5 Sio2-lim5, chhiann2 li2 kho2-lin5 goa2!¡¨ Khiok Sio2-lim5 tioh8-kiann, kin2-kin2 chiong hit e5 chinn5-tang5-a2 lam2 tiau5 teh, kong2, ¡§Phah-sng2, phah-sng2, che si7 goa2 e5 chinn5, bo5-ai3 hou7 li2!¡¨ Hit-ui7 heng5-iong5 thang kiann e5 lau7-lang5 tit8-tit8 pek oa2, hou7 Sio2-lim5 thoe3 kau3 long2 bo5 ui7. Kou-put-chiong, in-ui7 kiann-hiann5, Sio2-lim5 chiu7 koh khui chinn5-tang5-a2, tui3 hit lai7-bin7 chhiau-chhoe7 chit8-tiunn phoa3-noa7, beh tng7 cho3 koeh8 e5 gin5-phio3 hiat hou7 i.
Hit e5 lau7-lang5 chiu7 pian3-choe3 chit8 e5 chin sui2 e5 thinn-sai3, tui3 Sio2-lim5 seh-sia7 lai5 pian3 bo5-khi3. Sio2-lim5 koh khai-si2 ui7-tioh8 hit-tiunn phoa3-noa7 e5 gin5-phio3 lai5 siong-sim, tng i teh khoann3 hiah e5 gin5-phio3 e5 si5, hut-jian5 hiah e5 gin5-phio3 long2 khai-si2 sinn thang5, thang kiann e5 thang5 chit8-chiah chit8-chiah tui3 hit e5 tang5-a2 lai7 so5 chhut-lai5, au7-lai5 chiu7 so5 moa2 i e5 chhng5-teng2 kap pang5-keng, tit8-kau3 hiah e5 chinn5 long2 oan5-choan5 pian3-choe3 thang5.
Bo5 ku2 hiah e5 thang5 chiu7 tiong2-toa7 khi2-lai5 khai-si2 beh chiah8 Sio2-lim5 e5 bah. Sio2-lim5 kiann kau3 chau2 long2 bo5 lou7, i phe-mia7 teh chau2, hiah e5 thang5 tit8-tit8 teh tui-jiok. Ti3-kau3 Sio2-lim5 ti7 chau2 bo5 lou7 e5 si5 soa3 poah8-loh8 ti7 chit8 e5 ou-am3 e5 chhim-khinn. Sio2-lim5 khoann3-kinn3 hit e5 chhim-khinn e5 lai7-bin7 long2 si7 tun2 moa2 hu2-pai7 sinn-sian e5 chinn5-kak-a2 kap phoa3-noa7 e5 chinn5-phio3, Sio2-lim5 khoann3-liau2 chin kiann. Bo5-ku2 ko2-jian5 tui3 hiah e5 chinn5 e5 e7-bin7 u7 bu5-sou3-ban7 e5 chinn5-thang5, so5 chhut-lai5 beh chiah8 Sio2-lim5 e5 bah, Sio2-lim5 hou7 hiah e5 thang5 ka7 i so5 kau3 moa2 sin-khu, chiu7 kiann-hiann5 hoah kio3 kong2, ¡§Kiu3 goa2 lah, kiu3 goa2 lah, goa2 m7-ai3 chinn5 lah!¡¨
U7 nng7 e5 chheng7 peh8-sann e5 thinn-sai3 chhut-hian7 ti7 thinn-nih8, tui3 i kong2, ¡§Tang3-sng e5 Sio2-lim5, li2 ai3 goan2 ka7 li2 choe3 sim2-mih8?¡¨ Sio2-lim5 jin7-chhut hit nng7-ui7 chiu7-si7 khit-chiah8 kap lau7-lang5, chiu7 hoann-hi2 tui3 in kiu5 kong2, ¡§Chhiann2 lin2 kiu3 goa2 thoat-li7 chit e5 chinn5-thang5 e5 chhim-khinn!¡¨ Hit nng7-ui7 thinn-sai3 chiu7 chiong Sio2-lim5 hou7 in phoa3-noa7 e5 chinn5-phio3 theh8 ti7 chhiu2-nih8, tui7 loh8-khi3, chhiann2 Sio2-lim5 tioh8 khinn5 ti7 hit e5 chinn5-phio3, lai5 thoat-li7 chhim-khinn. Sio2-lim5 kin2-kin2 chit8-chhiu2 khi3 khinn5 ti7 chit-tiunn chinn5-phio3, khoann3-tioh8 hit e5 phoa3-noa7 beh tng7 e5 chinn5-phio3, hit-si5 Sio2-lim5 chiah hou7-hoe2, i an2-choann2 bo5 eng7 khah che7, khah ho2 e5 chinn5-phio3 hiat hou7 in, hit tiunn chinn5-phio3 si7 hiah-nih8 kho3 put-chu7, hiah-nih8 bo5 ng3-bang7.
I hou7-hoe2 koh hou7-hoe2 soa3 chek-pi7 ka-ki7 e5 tang3-sng, iau2-ku2 i khinn5 ti7 hit e5 chinn5-phio3, ng3-bang7 hit e5 chinn5-phio3 bo5 tng7-khi3. I e5 sin-khu u7 phu5 ti7 khong-tiong, chinn5-phio3 chiam7-chiam7 beh tng7 khi3 lah, hit e5 si5 chit8-tiunn5 thang-kiann, kin2-tiunn e5 si5-kan. Ko2-jian5 kau3 ti7 poann3 khong-tiong e5 si5 hiah e5 chinn5-phio3 chiu7 tng7-khi3, i chiu7 koh siak loh8-khi3 lah.
Sio2-lim5 ti7 toa7 kiann-hiann5 e5 si5 lai5 chhinn2 khi2-lai5, chiah chai-iann2 goan5-lai5 si7 teh choe3-bang7. I kin2-kin2 khoann3 i e5 chinn5-tang5-a2, iau2-ku2 ti7 i e5 sin-pinn, hiah-e5 chinn5 ia7 long2 bo5 sit bo5 khi3, i khai-si2 tui3 hiah e5 chinn5 u7 chit8-chiong2 e5 put-an. Chong2-si7 kau3 le2-pai3-jit8, tang3-sng e5 Sio2-lim5 chiu7 theh8 i e5 chinn5-tang5-a2 khi3 hian3 hou7 Chu2, thang pang-chan7 hit nng7-ui7 kho2-lin5 e5 lang5, i2-au7 lang5 chiu7 m7-bat koh kio3 i ¡§tang3-sng e5 Sio2-lim5¡¨ lah. (Ng5. L. L.)
