Kim-ku3: Sun7-than3 Siong7-te3 khah ke3-thau5 ti7 sun7-than3 lang5, si7 hap8-gi5. (Heng7-toan7 5:29)
U7 chit8 e5 gin2-na2 mia5 kio3 Chu2-hui7 khi3 goa7-kok thak8-chheh, tai7-seng bo5 peng5-iu2, chin bo5 phoann7, i e5 pa-pa kap ma-ma long2 bo5 kap i khi3, i chin ai3 u7 peng5-iu2, au7-lai5 chiu7 chiam7-chiam7 kap tong5-oh8 sek8-sai7, bo5-ku2 chiu7 pinn3 chin che7 peng5-iu2, iah8 u7 ho2 e5, iah8 u7 phainn2 e5, Chu2-hui7 e5 lau7-pe7 siong5-siong5 sia2 phoe hou7 i, ka7 i kong2, ¡§Li2 m7-thang kap peng5-iu2 khi3 poah8 pai5-a2, m7-thang khoann3 m7 ho2 e5 tian7-iann2, m7-thang ka-ki7 chit8 e5 khi3 iu5-eng2, li2 tioh8 khi3 le2-pai3, iah8 tioh8 khin5-khin5 thak8-chheh, iah8 tioh8 tu2-ho2 e5 un7-tong7 kap hioh-khun3.¡¨ Chu2-hui7 chai i e5 pa-pa kap ma-ma si7 se3-kai3 siong7 te7-it thiann3 i e5 lang5, i siunn7 kong2 sui-jian5 pe7-bo2 bo5 ti7 i e5 sin-pinn, iau2-ku2 goa2 na7 thiann in e5 oe7 pa-pa ma-ma tek-khak chin hoann-hi2, i iah8 chai sun7-than3 pe7-bo2 chiu7-si7 iu2-hau3, sou2-i2 i siong5-siong5 siunn7-khi2 i e5 pa-pa sou2 sia2 e5 phoe.
U7 chit8-jit8 i e5 phainn2 peng5-iu2 lai5 beh chio i khi3 poah8 pai5-a2, tit8-tit8 ka7 i chio, chong2-si7 Chu2-hui7 kong2 goa2 e5 lau7-pe7 kio3 goa2 m7-thang, sou2-i2 goa2 m7 kap li2 khi3, koh chit8-pai2 i e5 peng5-iu2 lai5 beh koh chio i khi3 khoann3 tian7-iann2, Chu2-hui7 chiu7 ka7 i kong2 goa2 e5 lau7-pe7 sia2 phoe lai5 kio3 goa2 tioh8 khin5-khin5 thak8-chheh, koh lan2 kho2-chhi3 teh-beh kau3 la3, goan2 m7-ai3 khi3, hit e5 peng5-iu2 chiu7 chin siu7-khi3, bo5-ai3 kap Chu2-hui7 cho3 peng5-iu2, hit e5 phainn2 peng5-iu2 chiu7 khi3 chio chin che7 peng5-iu2 kap Chu2-hui7 phainn2, Chu2-hui7 e5 sim chin kan-khou2, chong2-si7 i chai sun7-than3 lau7-pe7 e5 oe7 si7 khah tioh8, au7-lai5 i sui-jian5 bo5 chin che7 e5 peng5-iu2, iau2-ku2 i jin7-chin thak8-chheh, kau3-boe2 cho3 chin gau5 e5 phok-su7, i si7 chit8-ui7 sun7-than3 pe7-bo2 e5 lang5, Siong7-te3 u7 chiok-hok i chin seng5-kong.
Lan2 e5 Seng3-keng u7 ka3-si7 lan2, sun7-than3 Siong7-te3 khah koe3-thau5 ti7 sun7-than3 lang5 si7 hap8-gi5, i3-su3 si7 thiann Siong7-te3 e5 oe7 khah tioh8, thiann lang5 e5 oe7 khah m7-tioh8, Siong7-te3 chiu7-si7 lan2 thinn-teng2 e5 lau7-pe7, I u7 kia3 phoe lai5 hou7 lan2, chiu7-si7 Seng3-keng, Siong7-te3 e5 oe7 long2 ki3 ti7 Seng3-keng, lan2 na7 sun7-than3 Thinn-pe7 kiam2-chhai2 oe7 hou7 lang5 oan3-hin7, hou7 lang5 me7, chong2-si7 lan2 na7 oh8 Chu2-hui7 teh sun7-than3 i e5 lau7-pe7 e5 ka3-si7 kau3-boe2 lan2 e5 Thinn-pe7 beh chiok-hok lan2, lan2 tioh8 ho2-tann2 tioh8 oe7 ki3-tit Seng3-keng e5 oe7 kong2, ¡§Sun7-than3 Siong7-te3 khah koe3-thau5 ti7 sun7-than3 lang5 si7 hap8-gi5. (T. K. C.)
