Kim-ku3: Tiam3 ti7 siunn2-su3 goa2 khui3-lat8 e5, goa2 su7-su7 long2 oe7. (Hui-lip8-pi2 4:13)
Sio2 peng5-iu2 li2 ka-ki7 bat siunn7, li2 si7 chin loan2-jiok8, a2-si7 chin u7 lek8-liong7? Kiam2-chhai2 u7 lang5 ka-ki7 bat siunn7 i si7 chin u7 lek8-liong7, ki5-sit8 bo5-iann2. Li2 e7-ki3-tit koe3-khi3 8 geh8, Tiong-pou7 e5 toa7 chui2-chai a2-be7? Goa2 pun2-sin u7 khi3 khoann3 hiah e5 tu2-tioh8 chai-e7 e5 lang5, soa3 phoe3-un7 kiu3-che3-phin2 khi3 hou7 in. Khi3 kau3-ui7 chit8-e7 khoann3, u7 sou2-chai7 kui e5 chng-sia7 lau5 liau2-liau2, chhu3 long2 to2, lian5 tek-pho7, toa7-chhiu7 ia7 long2 khau khi2-lai5, chui2-chun3 eng7 chui2-ni5 choe3 e5 chui2-mng5, kio5-niu5, lian5 thih-kio5 to chhoah tng7 lau5-khi3.
Goa2 ia7 bat khoann3 hong-thai au7 e5 cheng5-keng2, phai3-chhut-sou2 e5 cheng-thah, a2-si7 tian7-lek8 tian7-soann3 e5 thih-thah, hou7 hong chhoe, soa3 chhin-chhiunn7 iu5-chiah8-koe2 an2-ni kng2-lun2-chun7 to2 ti7 thou5-kha. Ah! Li2 siunn7 Siong7-te3 e5 khui3-lat8 e5 thang kiann. (ti7 Hoa-lian5 e5 su7)
Koh bat khoann3 ti7 chit8-am3 tng lang5 teh khun3 e5 tiong-kan, Siong7-te3 eng7 toa7-hong kng2 khi2 thou5-soa lai5 kham3 chit8 e5 tek-ui5, chhin-chhiunn7 an2-ni goa2 bat khoann3 Hong-oan2 (cha2 kio3-choe3 Hoan-a2-oah) hu7-kin7 e5 chng-sia7 hou7 thou5-soa kham3-khi3. Li2 siunn7 lang5 ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 bin7-cheng5 u7 sim2-mih8 lek8-liong7 a2-bo5? Bo5, oan5-choan5 bo5.
Sou2-i2 lang5 be7-tit ti2-tek8 Siong7-te3, chi2-u7 sun7-hok8 na7-tiann7, siat-su2 li2 na7 sun7-hok8 Siong7-te3, lai5 tiam3 ti7 I e5 khui3-lat8, li2 chiu7 beh choe3-chhut li2 ka-ki7 siunn7 bo5 kau3 e5 su7. Li2 bat thiann Bi2-kok He-len-khe-lah sian-sinn e5 su7 a2-bo5? I si7 chit8 e5 thang kho2-lin5 se3-se3 e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2. Tng i se3-han3 e5 si5 chiu7 e2-kau2, chhinn-mi5, koh chhau3-hi7-lang5, li2 siunn7 che si7 joa7-nih8 chhi-chham2 e5 su7, chhinn-mi5 long2 bo5 khoann3-kinn3 sim2-mih8, to chhi-chham2 lah, soa3 ia7 bo5 thiann-kinn3 sim2-mih8 siann, koh e2-kau2 kan-khou2, pak-tou2 iau ia7 be7-hiau2 kong2. Lang5 na7 ka7 i hiat teh, i ka-ki7 ti7 hia na2 chun2 si2 e5 kan-khou2, kin-tu2 ia7 bo5 khoann3-kinn3 sim2-mih8 si3-pinn am3-bin5-bong. Koh ia7 bo5 thiann-kinn3 sim2-mih8, sim-koann siunn7 ia7 be7-hiau2 kong2, thong-jit8 kan-ta tiam7-tiam7 che7. Li2 siunn7 u7 kan-khou2 a2-bo5?
Na7 si7 i sin3 Siong7-te3, u7 thiann Chu2 Ia5-sou. I chhim-chhim oa2-kho3 Chu2, oa2-kho3 Siong7-te3 pang-chan7, bo5 loe2-chi3 lai5 lou2-lek8, kau3-boe2 i pinn3 chin gau5, i choe3 phok-su7, tann e7 kong2-oe7, kau3 tak8 sou2-chai7 kang2-ian2. I tu3 che7-che7 chheh, soa3 ui7-tioh8 phoa3-siunn3, chan5-hoe3 e5 phainn2-mia7-lang5 lai5 chou-chit che7-che7 kiu3-che3 e5 ki-koan, pinn3 choe3 tng chit e5 si5-tai7 m7-na7 Bi2-kok lang5 ia7-si7 se3-kai3 chit8 e5 chin toa7 e5 jin5-but8. Hian2-beng5 lang5 na7 tiam3 ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 un-tian2, khui3-lat8 e5 tiong-kan lai5 lou2-lek8 e5, ban7-su7 to e7.
Sio2 peng5-iu2 li2 sin3 Siong7-te3 mah? Li2 u7 khun3-lan5 mah? Kau-tai3 Chu2, sin3 I lai5 lou2-lek8, kau3-boe2 tek-khak e7 seng5-kong. (L. J. S.)
