Kim-ku3: Goan7 lin2 peng5-an; Goa2 chhe lin2, chhin-chhiunn7 Pe7 u7 chhe Goa2. (Iok-han7 20:21)
U7 chit8-pai2 kau3-hoe7 siu7 toa7 khun2-tiok8, hoe7-iu2 long2 chin kiann, in-ui7 na7 hou7 lang5 chai-iann2 i si7 thiann to7-li2 e5, lang5 chiu7 lai5 liah8 in, chiong in e5 ke-hoe2 long2 theh8-khi3, lang5 ia7 soa3 liah8-khi3 koainn ti7 kann-nih8, u7 e5 hou7 lang5 hai7-si2. Sou2-i2 in na7 beh keng3-pai3 Siong7-te3 long2 tioh8 koainn-mng5, ia7 chin kiann lang5 chai-iann2, Seng3-keng, seng3-si long2 te7 tiam3 lak8-te7-a2 lai7-bin7, m7-kann2 hou7 lang5 khoann3-kinn3.
Ti7 hit e5 kau3-hoe7 lai7 u7 3 e5 chheng-lian5 lang5, u7 chit8 e7-hng khi3 chhoe7 bok8-su, kong2, ¡§Bok8-su kiam2 u7-iann2 u7 Ia5-sou, na7 u7 thai2 bo5 tui3 thinn-teng2 chhe thinn-sai3 lai5 liah8 chiah e5 ham7-hai7 lan2 e5 lang5.¡¨ Bok8-su ka7 i kong2, Li2 m7-thang giau5-gi5 Siong7-te3, Siong7-te3 sou2 cho3 e5 tai7-chi3, bo5 chiau3 lang5 e5 sou2 siunn7, lin2 tioh8 m7-thang giau5-gi5, it-hoat pek-chhiat ki5-to2, chiu7 beh khoann3-kinn3 Siong7-te3 e5 koan5-leng5. Hit si5 bok8-su chiu7 chio hit 3 e5 chheng-lian5 lang5 kui7 ti7 pai3-tng5-thiann5 ki5-to2.
Hit 3 e5 chheng-lian5 chiau3 lun5 ki5-to2, lun5 liau2 bok8-su koh kong2 long2 chhut-siann pek-chhiat ki5-to2. 4 e5 lang5 e5 ki5-to2 hut-jian5 chhin-chhiunn7 kui-pah lang5 e5 siann, pai3-tng5 chhin-chhiunn7 jit8--si5 e5 khoan2, kng iann3-iann3. Thiann-kinn3 siann kong2, ¡§Goan7 lin2 tai7-ke peng5-an; Goa2 beh chhe lin2 khi3 si3-koe3 thoan5 hok-im.¡¨
Sann e5 chheng-lian5 e5 tiong-kan, ki5-tiong chit8 e5 kio3-cho3 Jin5-tek, chhut-siann hoah chhut-lai5, bok8-su ah...... si7 Ia5-sou e5 siann, oah8-oah8 e5 Chu2 ko2-jian5 bo5 li7-khui lan2, Ha-le-lu-iah, si3 e5 lang5 chhut-siann gim5-si.
