Ma2-le7 khi3 sin3 Ia5-sou liau2-au7, m7-na7 ka-teng5 e5 lang5 phainn2 khoan2-thai7 i, lian5 choan5 chng e5 lang5 long2 hoan2-tui3 kong-kek i.
Siong-sim e5 Ma2-le7 khiok chiau3-siong5 ti7 chng-lai7 teh be7 a-ma2 sou2 cho3 e5 chinn3-koe2, chong2-si7 tui3 i sin3 Ia5-sou liau2-au7 bo5 lang5 ai3 koh ka7 i boe2, ti3-kau3 i chi2 u7 khang-khang ti7 hit e5 han5-leng2 e5 ke-lou7 teh kiann5-seh8.
Ma2-le7 bo5 sit-bong7 bo5 hoe5-sim, sui-jian5 i tng2-khi3 it-teng7 oe7 hou7 a-ma2 me7 lai5 kui7 ti7 tng5-nih8, khiok i iau2-ku2 seng5-jin7 si7 chit8 e5 sin3 Ia5-sou e5 lang5. In-ui7 i chai-iann2 sin3 Ia5-sou chiah u7 Siong7-te3 e5 su3-hok.
I kiann5 koe3 chap8-hoe3 tiam3 e5 a-peh e5 mng5-khau2 koe3-khi3 e5 si5, a-peh chiu7 leng2-chhio3 i kong2, ¡§Se3-se3 e5 poe7-kau3-chia2.¡¨ I tui3 piann2-tiam3 e5 a-po5 e5 mng5-khau2 koe3 e5 si5 a-po5 chiu7 bi3-chhui3 ka7 keh-piah e5 lang5 kong2, ¡§M7-chiann5-kui2, sin3 Ia5-sou u7 sim2-mih8 li7-ek.¡¨ I kiann5 koe3 phah-thih e5 a-chek e5 tiam3-khau2 koe3-khi3 e5 si5, a-chek chiu7 kap tang5-phoann7 e5 ta-pou-lang5 kong2-oe7 lai5 thiau-lan5 i, ¡§Sin3 Ia5-sou m7-bian2 be7 koe2 ho2 lah, Ia5-sou oe7 siunn2-su3 lah.¡¨ Be7-chhai3 e5 a-chim2, be7-bah e5 lau7- a-peh long2 si7 lau7-iunn7 tui3 i chin hoan2-kam2. Lian5 ke-lou7 e5 gin2-na2 ia7 thi2-chhio3 i soa3 ka7 i phui3-noa7, ui7-tioh8 an2-ni kau3 chin am3, Ma2-le7 e5 koe2 iau2-boe7 be7 khi3. Ma2-le7 m7-kann2 tng2-khi3 chi2-u7 khang-khang teh kiann5.
I kiann5 kau3 ti7 chit8 e5 an-cheng7 e5 sip8-ji7-lou7 thau5 e5 si5, u7 tu2-tioh8 chit8 e5 pai2-kha e5 ta-pou-lang5, poah8-to2 ti7 lou7-nih8 teh peh boe7 khi2-lai5, Ma2-le7 kin2-kin2 pang3 i e5 koe2-siunn-a2, lai5 hu5-chou7 hit e5 pai2-kha e5 lang5 kau3 ti7 lou7-pinn e5 chioh8-teng2. ¡§A-peh, li2 an2-choann2 tioh8 bo5?¡¨ Ma2-le7 an2-ni mng7 i. ¡§Goa2 si7 chit8 e5 chhut-goa7 lang5, goa2 i2-keng bo5 lat8 thang kiann5 lah.¡¨ Ma2-le7 khoann3 i pak-tou2 chin iau e5 khoan2, chiu7 theh8 i e5 chinn3-koe2 khi2-lai5 hou7 i chiah8. ¡§Chin to-sia7, li2 si7 choe3 ho2-sim e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2, goa2 ku2-ku2 kiann5-iu5 teh chhoe7 chit-khoan2 e5 lang5, tann goa2 bo5 chinn5 thang hou7 li2, chi2-u7 chiong chit-pau le2-mih8 sang3 li2, chit e5 le2-mih8 tui3 ti7 kut-lat8, ho2-sim e5 lang5 si7 chin u7 li7-ek, tui3 ti7 pin5-toann7, phainn2-sim e5 lang5 chiu7 bo5 u7 lou7-eng7.¡¨
Kau3-boe2 Ma2-le7 chin hoann-hi2 toa3 hit e5 le2-mih8 tng2-khi3 chhu3-nih8. A-ma2 chiap tioh8 hit pau le2-mih8, ka7 i thau2-khui lai5 khoann3, goan5-lai5 si7 kim-koe-chi2, ¡§U7 sim2-mih8 lou7-eng7!¡¨ A-ma2 chiu7 chiong hiah e5 hiat tui3 au7-bin7 tiann5 khi3.
